Subject: [PATCH] Add KAXIS Factory 10 kanban gates

---
 hermes_cli/kanban_db.py                       | 347 ++++++++++++++++
 hermes_cli/main.py                            |   4 +-
 .../hermes_cli/test_kaxis_factory_v35_gate.py | 382 ++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 732 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
